    "body": "With this command it didn't work:\r\n```\r\ndocker run -d \\\r\n        --name beacon \\\r\n        --network host \\\r\n        --restart always \\\r\n        -v $(pwd)/.lighthouse:/root/.lighthouse \\\r\n        lighthouse:local \\\r\n        lighthouse --testnet pyrmont bn --target-peers 20 --metrics --disable-upnp --staking --http-address 127.0.0.1\r\n```\r\nWith this it works:\r\n```\r\ndocker run -d \\\r\n\t--name beacon \\\r\n\t--network host \\\r\n\t--restart always \\\r\n\t-v $(pwd)/.lighthouse:/root/.lighthouse \\\r\n\tlighthouse:local \\\r\n\tlighthouse --testnet pyrmont bn --target-peers 20 --metrics --datadir /root/.lighthouse/pyrmont --disable-upnp --staking --http-address 127.0.0.1\r\n```",
